# ORIG TITLE    Dépardieu becomes a resident of Saransk, central Russia . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Actor Gérard Dépardieu has registered as a resident of Saransk, in the central Russian region of Mordovia. He has already threatened to give up his French citizenship due to high taxation. He was issued a Russian passport in January. Dépardieu’s new address is on Demokratichnaya (Democratic) Street, which he told Russian television he found “symbolic”. 
